{"id": 818, "genre": 1000, "title": "【现代病】你也有“原创恐惧”吗？", "description": "原创恐惧指的是：不管怎么发状态、贴图都觉得没自信，好像有点矫情，像在刷存在感，怕被吐槽，也怕没人点赞。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5667, "comment_count": 34, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021838089bSsZWXwJN14xvLO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-19T01:06:07Z", "questions": [{"id": 711, "title": "【现代病】你也有“原创恐惧”吗？", "content": "现代病之你也有原创恐惧吗？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 50740, "content": "不是让人拍大腿的好东西憋死都不会发出来", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183209xXqDNCOYPRezWpjr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50742, "content": "打好了140字，结果一个一个删掉", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183209NU91wbx5y0DoWgu8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50745, "content": "对热点怒写5000字…算了，还是转大V的", "image": "img/option/option/201607021832168o2nbOA1VpydUTEI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50746, "content": "发条状态要斟酌半小时以上", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183217ZEpkn8cb6HLFIYQm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50750, "content": "隔一分钟就赶紧看下有没有人赞", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183217Xqy7Gz9vNjaMYu1H.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50752, "content": "十分钟都没有人赞就赶紧删了", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183218SqzKAC1FG4R7Lxd6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50753, "content": "所以你看到，500条有490条都是转发的", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183218DGUXoWBCJZTkpNtL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 50755, "content": "没有赞也不怕，反正是别人写的", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183218LnBWSMmKo4wDeaxT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}